%N A393691 Decimal expansion of Integral_{x=1..e} log(log(x))/(1+x^2) dx (negated).
%C A393691 For comments see A388042.
%F A393691 Equals real part of Integral_{x=1/e..1} log(log(x))/(1+x^2) dx (negated).
